ivardefs.name: basedOn_
ivardefs.desc: A plan, proposal or order that is fulfilled in whole or in part by this event.

ivardefs.name: category_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates where the food or fluid was  consumed or prescribed.

ivardefs.name: consumedItem_
ivardefs.desc: What food or fluid product or item was consumed.

ivardefs.name: dateAsserted
ivardefs.desc: The date when the Nutrition Intake was asserted by the information source.

ivardefs.name: derivedFrom_
ivardefs.desc: Allows linking the NutritionIntake to the underlying NutritionOrder, or to other information, such as AllergyIntolerance, that supports or is used to derive the NutritionIntake.

ivardefs.name: encounter
ivardefs.desc: The encounter that establishes the context for this NutritionIntake.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifiers associated with this Nutrition Intake that are defined by business processes and/or used to refer to it when a direct URL reference to the resource itself is not appropriate. They are business identifiers assigned to this resource by the perfo

ivardefs.name: informationSource
ivardefs.desc: The person or organization that provided the information about the consumption of this food or fluid. Note: Use derivedFrom when a NutritionIntake is derived from other resources.

ivardefs.name: ingredientLabel_
ivardefs.desc: Total nutrient amounts for the whole meal, product, serving, etc.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Provides extra information about the Nutrition Intake that is not conveyed by the other attributes.

ivardefs.name: partOf_
ivardefs.desc: A larger event of which this particular event is a component or step.

ivardefs.name: reasonCode_
ivardefs.desc: A reason for why the food or fluid is /was consumed.

ivardefs.name: reasonReference_
ivardefs.desc: Condition or observation that supports why the food or fluid is /was consumed.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: A code representing the patient or other source's judgment about the state of the intake that this assertion is about.  Generally, this will be active or completed.

ivardefs.name: statusReason_
ivardefs.desc: Captures the reason for the current state of the NutritionIntake.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: The person, animal or group who is/was consuming the food or fluid.

properties.desc: A record of food or fluid that is being consumed by a patient.   A NutritionIntake may indicate that the patient may be consuming the food or fluid now or has consumed the food or fluid in the past.  The source of this information can be the patient, sign
